hadiths[27]{hadithnumber,text}:
3391,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dunyawi chizon mein sey biwi aur khushbu mujhey bahut pasand hain. aur meri aakhon ki thandak namaz mein rakh di gaee hai.
3392,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (dunyawi chizon mein) mujhey biwi aur khushbu bahut pasand hain lekin meri aakhon ki thandak namaz mein muzmir hai.
3393,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke biwiyon key baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko koi chiz ghodon sey badh kar pasand nahin thi.
3394,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ki do biwiyan hon aur wo eik ki taraf ziyada jhukaaw rakhta ho to qiyamat key din is tarah aayega ke us ka eik pehlu jhuka huwa hoga.
3395,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni biwiyon mein insaf key sath baari muqarrar kartey, phir farmatey : aey Allah ! ye to mera kaam hai jiska mujhey ikhtiyar hai. jis chiz mein tujhey ikhtiyar hai aur main be-bas hun, us barey mein mujh par giraft na farmana. Hammad bin Zaid ney is riwayat ko munqata' sanad sey bayan kiya hai."
3396,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki dusri azwaje-mutahrat (biwiyon) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bheja. unhoney aap sey andar aaney ki ijazat talab ki jab ke us waqt aap merey sath meri chadar mein letey huye they. aap ney unhen ijazat di. unhoney aa kar kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap ki azwaje-mutahrat (biwiyon) ney mujhey aap key paas bheja hai. unka mutalba hai ke aap Abu-Qahaafa ki beti (Hazrat Aaisha ) key barey mein insaf sey kaam lein. main khamosh thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : aey beti ! kya tujhey us sey mohabbat nahin jis sey mujhey mohabbat hai? unhoney kaha : kyon nahin? farmaya : phir is (Aaisha) sey mohabbat rakh. Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ye baat suni to uth khadi huin aur wapis ja kar aap ki azwaje-mutahrat (biwiyon) ko apni baat aur aap ka jawab sab kuchh bata diya. wo kehney lagin : hamarey khayal main tum ney hamein koi faeyda nahin pahunchaya. dobara Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas jaao aur aap sey kaho ke aap ki biwiyan aap sey Abu-Qahaafa ki beti key barey mein insaf ki talabgar hain. Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : nahin, Allah ki qism ! main aap sey kabhi bhi uski baabat koi baat nahin karungi. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaje-mutahrat ney Hazrat Zainab bin Jahash (aap ki biwi) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bheja. aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki wahid biwi thin jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key nazdik merey barabar martaba rakhti thin aur mainey kabhi koi aurat aisi nahin dekhi jo Hazrat Zainab sey badh kar deeni lihaz sey nek, Allah Taala sey darney wali sach bolney wali, sila-rehmi karney wali, ziyada sadqa karney wali aur apney aap ko sadqey aur neki key kaam mein khapaa deney wali ho. albatta un ki tabiat mein kuchh tezi thi jo jald hi khatam ho jaya karti thi. unhoney bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey andar aaney ki ijazat talab ki jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key sath un ki chadar mein isi tarah letey huye they, jis tarah Hazrat Fatima key aaney key waqt they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen ijazat di to unhoney aa kar kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ki azwaje-mutahrat (biwiyon) ney mujhey aap key paas bheja hai. wo aap sey Abu-Qahaafa ki beti ki baabat insaf ki talabgar hain, phir wo mujhey bura bhala kehney lagin aur bahut der tak kehti rahin. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf dekh rahi thi aur muntazir thi ke aap aankh key isharay hi sey mujhey jawab deney ki ijazat den lekin Zainab baaz na aai yahan tak ke mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke ab agar main badla lun to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) napasand nahin farmaeyngey. chunanche jab main shuru hui to mainey unhen eik minat bhi na bolney diya yahan tak ke mainey unhen daba liya aur chup kara diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (muskuraatey huye) farmaya : bilashuba ye Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti hai."
3397,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey is sey milti julti riwayat aati hai ke azwaje-mutahrat (paak biwiyon) ney Hazrat Zainab (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja. unhoney andar aaney ki ijazat talab ki. aap ney ijazat di to unhoney andar aa kar kaha : … الخ. Ma'mar ney un dono (Saleh aur Shoaib) ki mukhalifat ki hai. us ney ye riwayat an Zohri an Urwa an Aaisha ki sanad sey bayan ki hai.
3398,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki (dusri) azwaje-mutahrat (biwiyan) ikhatti huin aur unhoney Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja aur unhen kaha : (aap sey ja kar kahu) aap ki biwiyan aap sey Abu-Qahaafa ki beti key silsiley mein insaf ki duhaai deti hain. Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huin to aap Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key sath un ki chadar mein letey huye they. unhoney aa kar aap sey kaha : aap ki biwiyon ney mujhey aap ki taraf bheja hai. wo aap sey Abu-Qahaafa ki beti key silsiley mein insaf ki duhaai deti hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein farmaya : kya tujhey mujh sey mohabbat hai? wo kehney lagen : zarur. aap ney farmaya : phir to is (Aaisha) sey mohabbat rakh. wo unkey paas wapis chali gaeen aur unhen aap ka jawab suna diya. wo kehney lagin : tum ney kuchh nahin kiya, dobara jaao. unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism ! main Hazrat Aaisha key masley mein kabhi bhi aap key paas dobara nahin jaaungi. haqiqat ye hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sahih beti thin, phir unhoney Hazrat Zainab binte Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ko bheja. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaje-mutahrat mein sey yehi wo zauja mutahra thin jo merey barabar darja rakhti thin. wo aa kar kehney lagin : aap ki biwiyon ney mujhey aap key paas bheja hai. wo aap sey Abu-Qahaafa ki beti ki baabat insaf ki talabgar hain, phir wo meri taraf mutawajjeh ho kar mujhey bura bhala kehney lagin. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key hukm ka intizar karney lagi. main aap ki aankh ki taraf dekh rahi thi ke aap mujhey badla leney ki ijazat detey hain ya nahin. wo mujhey bura bhala kehti rahin yahan tak ke mujhey andaza ho gaya ke ab agar main un sey badla lun to aap napasand nahin farmaeyngey, phir main un ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar unhen jawab deney lagi. thodi der mein mainey unhen chup kara diya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen (chup dekh kar) farmaya : ye Abu-Bakar ki beti hai. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mainey koi aurat Zainab sey badh kar nek, ziyada sadqey karney wali, sila-rehmi karney wali aur har us kaam mein apney aap ko khapaa deney wali jis sey Allah Taala ka qurb hasil kiya ja sakey, nahin dekhi magar un mein kuchh tezi aur turshi thi jo jald hi khatam ho jaya karti thi. Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke ye riwayat khata hai aur sahih riwayat pehli hai."
3399,Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki fazilat tamam aurton par aisey hai jaisey sareed ki fazilat dusrey khaanon par.
3400,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dusri aurton par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki fazilat aisey hai jaisey dusrey khaanon par sareed ko fazilat hasil hai.
3401,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Umme-Salma ! mujhey Aaisha ki baabat takleef na dey. Allah ki qism ! uskey ilawa tum mein sey kisi key lihaaf mein mujhey wahi nahin aai.
3402,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki biwiyon ney mujh sey kaha ke tum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey baat karo ke log qasdan Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki baari key din aap ko tohfey bhejtey hain. aap sey kaho ke Hazrat Aaisha ki tarah hum bhi us fazilat ki khahish mand hain. mainey is barey mein aap sey baat ki. aap ney koi jawab na diya. jab aap baari key lihaz sey merey paas aaye to mainey phir baat ki. aap ney phir jawab na diya. azwaje-mutahrat (paak biwiyon) ney mujh sey puchha : aap ney kya jawab diya? mainey kaha : kuchh bhi nahin. wo kehney lagin : tum aap sey bar-bar ye baat karti raho yahan tak ke aap jawab den. jab aap dobara merey paas aaye to mainey phir yehi baat kahi. aap ney farmaya : (Umme-Salma ! ) mujhey Aaisha key barey mein sataya na karo kyonkey jab main tum mein sey kisi key lihaaf mein hota hun to Aaisha key lihaaf key siwa mujh par kabhi wahi nahin utri. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke raawi Abda sey marwi ye dono hadeesein sahih hain.
3403,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke log qasdan apney tohfey Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki baari key din bheja kartey they. us sey unka maqsud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khushi aur raza-mandi ka husool tha.
3404,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke eik dafa Allah Taala ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf wahi nazil farmaaee. main bhi aap key sath thi. main uth gaee aur darmiyan wala darwaza band kar diya. jab aap sey wahi ki shiddat door hui to aap ney farmaya : aey Aaisha ! Jibril tujhey salam keh rahey hain.
3405,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey farmaya : Jibril alehissalam tujhey salam keh rahey hain. mainey jawaaban kaha : (و علیہ السلام ورحمۃ اللہ وبرکاتہ),''un par bhi salamti, rahmaten aur barkaten hon.''aap wo kuchh dekhtey hain ke hum nahin dekhtey."
3406,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Aaisha ! ye Jibril hain aur tujhey salam keh rahey hain. mazkura baala riwayat ki tarah. Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney farmaya : ye riwayat sahih hai. is sey pehli riwayat khata hai.
3407,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik Ummul-Mominin key paas they to dusri Ummul-Mominin ney eik piyaley mein koi khurdani (khane wali) chiz bheji. chunanche is (pehli Ummul-Mominin) ney qaasid key haath par zarab lagai to piyala gir kar toot gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney dono tukdey uthaey, eik ko dusrey key sath joda aur khana ikhatta kar key is mein dalney lagey aur farma rahey they : tumhari maa ko ghairat aa gaee, khaao. sab ney mil kar khaya, phir todney wali Ummul-Mominin apna piyala laeen. aap ney sahih piyala qaasid ko dey diya aur tootaa huwa todney wali key ghar rehney diya."
3408,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sahaba key liye apney piyaley mein koi khana ley kar (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key ghar) aayen. Hazrat Aaisha eik chadar odhey huye aayen. unkey haath main eik chhota sa patthar tha. unhoney us patthar sey piyala tod diya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney piyaley key dono tukdon ko joda aur aap farma rahey they : khana khaao. tumhari maa ko ghussa aa gaya. aap ney do dafa farmaya. phir aap ney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ka piyala ley kar Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key ghar bhej diya. aur Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ka (tootaa huwa) piyala Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko dey diya.
3409,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey koi aurat Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) jaisa khana pakaaney wali nahin dekhi. eik dafa unhoney khana tayyar kar key eik bartan mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf (merey ghar) bhej diya. main apney aap par zabt na kar saki. mainey wo bartan tod diya, phir mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us (bartan todney) ka kaffara puchha to aap ney farmaya : bartan jaisa bartan aur khaney jaisa khana."
3410,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Zainab binte Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) key paas (kuchh ziyada der) thehertey they ke unkey paas shehad peetey they. mainey aur Hafsa ney mansuba banaya ke hum mein sey jis key paas bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laeyn wo keh dey : main aap sey maghaafeer ki boo paati hun. aap ney maghaafeer khaya hai? phir aap un dono mein sey kisi key ghar tashrif ley gaey to us ney yehi kuchh aap sey keh diya. aap ney farmaya : nahin, mainey Zainab binte Jahash key yahan sey shehad piya hai, dobara nahin piyunga. phir aap par ye aayat utri : (یٰآَیُّھَا النَّبِیُّ لِمَ تُحَرِّمُ … ),''aey Nabi ! aap us chiz ko kyon haram kartey hain jisey Allah ney aap key liye halal rakha hai.''aagey farmaya : ( اِنْ تَتُوْبَآ اِلَی اللّٰہِ),''agar tum tauba karo … الخ.''is sey Aaisha aur Hafsa murad hain. aur : (وَاِذْ اَسَرَّالنَّبِیُّ اِلٰی بَعْضِ اَزْوَاجِہٖ حَدِیْثاً),''jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik biwi sey raz ki baat farmaee.'' us sey murad aap ka farman : balke mainey shehad piya hai … الخ hai."
3411,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki eik laundi thi jis sey aap sohbat kiya kartey they. lekin Hazrat Aaisha aur Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) aap ko majbur karti rahin yahan tak ke aap ney usey apney liye haram kar liya to Allah ney ye ""wahi"" utaari : (یٰآَیُّھَاالنَّبِیُّ لِمَ تُحَرِّمُ … ),''aey Nabi ! aap us chiz ko apney liye kyon haram qarar dey rahey hain jisey Allah Taala ney aap key liye halal rakha hai … .'' mukammal aayat."
3412,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eik dafa (raat ko) main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dhoondney lagi. to mainey apna haath aap key (sar key) baalon mein dakhil kar diya. aap ney farmaya : terey paas tera shetan aa gaya? mainey arz kiya : kya aap key liye koi shetan nahin hai? aap ney farmaya : kyon nahin? (merey sath bhi shetan hai) lekin Allah Taala ney uskey khilaf meri madad farmaee hai, lihaza main (us key asraat sey) mehfooz rehta hun."
3413,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke eik raat mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko mojud na paya to mainey samjha ke aap apni kisi biwi key yahan chaley gaey hain. mainey aap ko tatolna shuru kiya to pata chala ke aap to rukoo ya sajdey ki haalat mein hain. aap padh rahey they :(سُبْحَانَکَ وَبِحَمْدِکَ لاَ اِلٰہَ اِلاَّ أَنْتَ),''aey Allah ! to apni khoobiyon samet paak hai. terey siwa koi mabood nahin.'' mainey kaha : merey maa baap aap par qurban ! aap kaisey haal mein hain aur main kin tassawuraat mein ghaltaan hun."
3414,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eik raat mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko (apney qarib) mojud na paya to mainey samjha aap apni kisi aur biwi key paas chaley gaey hain. mainey (bahir nikal kar) aap ko dhoondaa, phir wapis aai to aap rukoo ya sajdey ki haalat mein they aur padh rahey they : (سُبْحَانَکَ وَبِحَمْدِکَ لاَ اِلٰہَ اِلاَّ أَنْتَ),''aey Allah ! to apni tamam khoobiyon samet pak hai. terey siwa koi bar-haq mabood nahin.'' mainey kaha : merey maa baap aap par qurban ! aap kis haal mein hain aur main kis khayal mein."
3415,"Muhammad bin Qais sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : kya main tumhen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka aur apna eik waqia na bayan karun? hamney kaha : kyon nahin? (zarur bayan karen.) wo farmaney lagin : eik raat jab meri baari thi to aap (Isha ki namaz sey) wapis tashrif laye to apney jootey utaar kar apney paaun key qarib rakh liye, apni chadar utaari aur apna tehband bistar par bichha liya aur itni der letey rahey ke aap ney samjha main so gaee hun, phir aap ney chupkey sey jootey pehney aur holey sey apni chadar uthai aur halkey sey darwaza khol kar nikal gaey aur baghair aahat kiye darwaza band kar diya. mainey fauran qamis pahni, odhni li, tehband kasaa aur aap key peechhey ho li. yahan tak ke aap Baqee al-gharqad mein pahunch gaey aur teen dafa aap ney apney dono haath uthaey (aur dua ki), aap bahut der khadey rahey, phir aap wapis mudey to main bhi mudi, aap kuch tez huye to main bhi tez chalney lagi, aap bhagney lagey to main bhi bhaagi, phir aap ney daud laga di to mainey bhi daud laga di. aur main aap sey pehley pahunch gaee. main hujrey mein dakhil ho kar abhi leti hi thi ke aap aa pahunchey aur farmaya : Aaisha ! tujhey kya huwa hai? pet phulaa huwa hai aur saans chadha huwa hai? mujhey bata dey warna bareek-been aur khabrdar (Allah) mujhey bata dega. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey maa baap aap par fidaa hon, phir mainey aap ko puri baat bata di. aap ney farmaya : tu hi wo saya tha jo mainey apney aagey aagey dekha? mainey kaha : ji haan. aap ney zor sey merey seeney mein haath maara jis sey mujhey sakht takleef hui. aap ney farmaya : kya to samajhti thi ke Allah aur us ka Rasool tujh par zulm kerengey? Hazrat Aaisha ney kaha : log jis qadr bhi baat chupaeyn Allah Taala jaan hi leta hai. aap ney farmaya : bilkul. aap ney farmaya : jab tu ney (mujhey uthtey) dekha tha us waqt Jibril alehissalam merey paas aaye they. chunkey to kapdey utaar chuki thi, is liye wo andar nahin aa saktey they. unhoney tujh sey chhupa kar mujhey aawaz di. mainey bhi tujh sey chhupa kar unhen jawab diya. main samajhta tha ke to so chuki hai, lihaza mainey tujhey jagaana munasib na samjha kyonkey mujhey khatra tha ke to akeli dareygi. unhoney mujhey hukm diya ke main Baqee walon key paas jaaun aur unkey liye bakhshish ki dua karun. Hujjaaj bin Muhammad ney (is hadees key raawi) ibne Wahab ki mukhalifat ki hai. us ney sanad yun bayan ki hai : an ibne Juraij, an ibne Abi Mulaika, an Muhammad bin Qais. (jab ke ibne Wahab ney ibne Juraij aur Muhammad bin Qais key darmiyan Abdullah bin Kasir ka wasta bayan kiya hai.)"
3416,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Qais bin Makhrima bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko hadees bayan kartey huye suna, unhoney farmaya : kya main tumhen apna aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka eik waqia na bayan karun? hamney kaha : kyon nahin ! (zarur bayan farmaeyn.) to unhoney farmaya : eik raat jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney merey yahaan raat guzari thi, aap (Isha ki namaz padh kar) tashrif laye, aap ney apney jootey (utaar kar) apney paon key qarib rakh liye, apni (oopper wali) chadar utaari aur apney tehband ka eik kinara apney bistar par bicha liya. aap itni der letey rahey ke aap ney samjha main so gaee hun (halanke main jaagti thi). phir aap ney chupkey sey jootey pehney, aahista sey chadar pakdi, holey sey darwaza khol kar nikley aur halkey sey darwaza band kar diya. mainey qamis pahni, odhni li aur tehband baandha aur aap key peechhey chal di, yahan tak ke aap Baqee mein pahunch gaey. aap ney teen dafa (bar-bar dua key liye) apney haath uthaey aur bahut der tak khadey rahey, phir aap wapis mudey, main bhi mudi, aap kuchh tez huye to main bhi tez ho li, aap bhagney lagey, mein bhi bhagney lagi. aap ney daud laga di, mainey bhi daud laga di aur main aap sey pehley ghar mein dakhil ho gaee. abhi main leti hi thi ke aap bhi pahunch gaey aur farmaya : Aaisha ! tujhey kya huwa? tera pet phulaa huwa hai aur saans chadha huwa hai? mainey kaha : kuchh bhi nahin. aap ney farmaya : mujhey bata dey warna bareek-bee khabar rakhney wala (Allah) mujhey bata dega. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey maa-baap aap par fidaa hon, phir mainey aap ko pura waqia bata diya. aap ney farmaya : achchhaa tu hi wo saya tha jisey mainey apney aagey aagey dekha? mainey kaha : ji haan. aap ney merey seeney mein is zor sey haath maara ke mujhey bahut takleef hui. phir aap ney mujhey farmaya : kya tu ney samjha ke Allah aur us ka Rasool tujh par zulm kerengey? mainey kaha : log Allah Taala sey jis qadr bhi baat chhupaeyn, Allah jaan hi leta hai. aap ney farmaya : bilkul. phir aap ney farmaya : jab tu ney (mujhey uthtey) dekha tha, us waqt Jibril alehissalam merey paas aaye they lekin wo andar nahin aa saktey they kyonkey to apney kapdey utaar chuki thi. chunanche unhoney tujh sey chhupatey huye mujhey aahista sey aawaz di aur mainey bhi tujh sey chhupatey huye aahista sey jawab diya. mera khayal tha ke to sau chuki hai aur mujhey khatra tha ke (agar tujhey jagaa diya to) akeli dareygi. to unhoney mujhey hukm diya ke main Baqee walon key paas ja kar unkey liye bakhshish ki dua karun. is riwayat ko Aasim ney an Abdullah bin Aamir an Aaisha ki sanad sey kuchh mukhtalif alfaz key sath bayan kiya hai."
3417,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey eik raat aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko mojud na paya. (phir raawi ney puri hadees bayan ki.)
